:::::::'''Young Master Gold:''' What would you like to know, dear guest? All this content should be put in the film, tweet~
:::::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} About Clock Garden...
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414034155-->
::::::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Clock Garden was the first paradise of Dreamville, it was designed by Clockie and built by myself, sweet~ Hmm, it truly is an ingenious design!
::::::::'''Young Master Gold:''' If the Great Tree is the most dazzling tree in Goldleaf Plaza... Then Clock Garden is the sweetest fruit the Great Tree has ever borne, tweet!
:::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} About the townspeople...
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414034158-->
::::::::'''Young Master Gold:''' The citizens of Dreamville are all fascinating fellows~ Of course, I am the most dazzling of them all~
::::::::'''Young Master Gold:''' I sometimes attend Miss Note's tea parties... Miss Note always prepares delicious berries and wonderful music. Hmm, I guess I would say that she is the second most dazzling citizen in Dreamville~
:::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} About Professor Owl...
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414034161-->
::::::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Hmm... Hmmmm! You know the great Professor Owl, too? The Professor is the smartest and strongest bird in the whole village! They are also the leader of us origami birds, tweet.
::::::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Legend has it that in the beginning, Professor Owl built Dreamville branch-by-branch all by themselves... What a great bird, tweet! I want to become an amazing bird like them, tweet!
::::::::'''Young Master Gold:''' I know that when that time comes, Professor Owl will praise me, too, tweet~
:::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
